text:
Anna Sieprath (born 26 November 1985 in Auckland) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships, 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2010 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup.
She was educated at Diocesan School for Girls, Auckland. She played for the University of Hawaii's women's water polo team.
